package:

  sha256: 1cf6a685f7e0af249febd52972bdaf6dc58fdc408a7c45c48912200522a58690

  number: 0

requirements:
  build:
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools
  run:
    - boto3
    - python >=3.6
    - numpy
    - diskcache
    - packaging
    - requests
    - imageio

test:
  imports:
    - slicedimage

about:
  home: https://github.com/spacetx/slicedimage

  license_file: LICENSE
